data.description: Just south of downtown, this fully remodeled house sitting on just under an acre is ready for its next owner. The current homeowners took this house all the way down to the studs and put in all new electrical, plumbing, repurposed wood flooring and the list goes on. The main level has a Bakers kitchen w/ 2 ovens, 2 refrigerators and a large walk in pantry. Just off the kitchen is a large dining room, office with 3/4 bath attached and laundry. You will also find a living room and a bedroom with an attached 1/2 bath. Upstairs there is a loft space and 2 beds/2 baths. The primary bath has 3 shower heads including a rain shower and teak shower walls. The hall bath features an amazing original clawfoot tub. Schedule your showing today to see everything this house has to offer.  All information obtained from seller and public records.
